history.content:
Hello Everyone,

My friends and I are trying to create a platform to help incoming freshmen with their transition to UC Berkeley this fall. We have designed a detailed outline for the project, but none of us are experienced when it comes to web design. If anybody is interested in volunteering and has experience in either front-end or back-end web design, your help would be much appreciated. Just to clarify, this is entirely voluntary (unpaid) work to help freshmen and transfer students with their transition to Berkeley.

Send me an email at mpaller@berkeley.edu if you are interested or have any questions!

Thank you!
